<div class="title">Delirium at Night</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-7</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=EuFiHel&Exact=1">EuFiHel</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; EuFiHel. "Delirium at Night: An Experience with 2C-T-7 (exp5276)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 27, 2001. erowid.org/exp/5276</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
